WEBVTT

00:00:58.915 --> 00:01:01.561
I upalila sam ga i čula:

00:01:02.061 --> 00:01:04.233
U Fergusonu, Missouriju,

00:01:04.233 --> 00:01:05.815
Michaela Browna

00:01:06.445 --> 00:01:08.665
18-godišnjeg crnca,

00:01:08.665 --> 00:01:14.564
nenaoružanog je upucao bijeli policajac,
i ležao je mrtav na tlu,

00:01:14.564 --> 00:01:18.478
njegova je krv tekla četiri sata

00:01:18.478 --> 00:01:22.993
dok su njegova baka i malena djeca i
susjedi gledali s užasom

00:01:22.993 --> 00:01:24.989
I pomislila sam,

00:01:26.019 --> 00:01:29.240
evo ga opet.

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.962
To nasilje, ta brutalnost protiv crnaca